        Returns the dataflow result for code fragment which contains given context

        Returns:

      • getExpressionRange

        public static LongRangeSet getExpressionRange(PsiExpression expression)
        Returns long range set for expression or null if range is unknown. This method first tries to compute expression using ConstantExpressionEvaluator and only then calls getDfType(PsiExpression).
        Parameters:
        expression - expression to get its range
        Returns:
        long range set
